}}'''邁爾祖格沙漠'''（Murzuq Desert，Idehan Murzuq，Idhan Murzuq）是[[利比亚|利比亚]]西南部的一片沙漠，為[[撒哈拉沙漠|撒哈拉沙漠]]的一部分，面积约58000平方公里<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://books.google.com/books?id=WOcUNbRUGtwC&pg=PA403&lpg=PA403&dq=%22Desert+Geomorphology%22+great+sand+sea&source=bl&ots=pzWXeCIPDv&sig=FDK0aAvYSit7JTsjYrrJsboFG9A&hl=en&sa=X&ei=h7_uU_-5J9a58gWV5YKoBQ&ved=0CBsQ6AEwAA#v=onepage&q=%22Desert%20Geomorphology%22%20great%20sand%20sea&f=false |title=Desert Geomorphology, p. 403 |access-date=2020-08-11 |archive-date=2020-04-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200410053143/https://books.google.com/books?id=WOcUNbRUGtwC&pg=PA403&lpg=PA403&dq=%22Desert+Geomorphology%22+great+sand+sea&source=bl&ots=pzWXeCIPDv&sig=FDK0aAvYSit7JTsjYrrJsboFG9A&hl=en&sa=X&ei=h7_uU_-5J9a58gWV5YKoBQ&ved=0CBsQ6AEwAA#v=onepage&q=%22Desert%20Geomorphology%22%20great%20sand%20sea&f=false |dead-url=no }}</ref>。它的名稱來源自[[费赞|费赞]]的[[迈尔祖格|迈尔祖格]]。它与撒哈拉沙漠南部被[[提贝斯提高原|提贝斯提高原]]和[[阿杰尔高原|阿杰尔高原]]隔开。

